title: Military Academy with That Tenth Avenue Gang
text:
Military Academy with That Tenth Avenue Gang is a 1950 American comedy drama film directed by <a href="D.%20Ross%20Lederman">D. Ross Lederman</a>,
and starring <a href="Stanley%20Clements">Stanley Clements</a>, <a href="Danny%20Welton">Danny Welton</a>, and <a href="Gene%20Collins">Gene Collins</a>.
